{
  "stem": "15694.7",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was still the-- it didn't-- it was probably the-- the Polish quarters.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think according to the-- what I see of the sketch map, it's probably what they have on the sketch map as the Polish quarters, which I will show at the end.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now-- but the-- but the wires there, as I say, in-- in the sketch map, extended.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were a few mistakes in that sketch map which I have explained in my book.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For instance, behind the metal workshop, they put the wires sort-- very near in the sketch, whereas they must have been some distance because between the barracks and-- and the-- and the wire and where the watch-- watchtowers were, there must have been a distance.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because the mountains of-- of--of metal there which we had to select from, and to get to work-- to work with in the-- in the metal workshop.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyway, next morning, we were sent away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I would say if ever a hunch paid off, it was my father's.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because what I'm going to tell you now is no less than going from hell into paradise.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were only 50 in a wagon, and we went to a place called Kielce.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just-- just always being the last in line, so to say.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We came to the last wagons.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went into the last wagons.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At a later stage, this being last proved actually no less than fatal.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in this case, it was luck.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The last two wagons, the train stopped.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The last two wagons were emptied.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were 100 people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was-- there wasn't the usual call, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was just get out, you know, the normal sort of two wagons.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Please come-- you know, not-- I don't know if they said please.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
